tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE error_correction_results (record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
experiment_name VARCHAR(255),
error_rate FLOAT,
correction_success BOOLEAN,
timestamp TIMESTAMP)

CREATE TABLE error_correction_results (
    result_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    error_type VARCHAR(50),
    error_rate DECIMAL,
    correction_success BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE error_correction_methods (
    method_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    method_name VARCHAR(100),
    method_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE experimental_data (
    data_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    qubit_number INT,
    result_id INT,
    method_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE error_correction_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    quantum_circuit_name VARCHAR(255),
    error_type VARCHAR(50),
    error_probability FLOAT,
    error_correction_success BOOLEAN
);
